title: Independent candidate Mehboob Sultan wins NA-108 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Mohammad Mehboob Sultan has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-108, Jhang I by securing 169,578 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Makhdum Syed Faisal Saleh Hayat Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz candidate, who bagged 134,270 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 59.32 percent.
